commit.message: Replace redis with ioredis node module
Unlock use of secret in case of bad requests

state of server (closed/closing/etc)

new "listen" option (default: true)

server now inherits from EventEmitter (events: "error", "ready")
Tests for Server.createSignature, added support for non-hex key

API key authorization via HMAC

Allows other (even offline!) apps to create authorized lnurls

Removed POST /lnurl end-point

Removed "apiKeyHash" option and replaced with "auth.apiKeys"

generateApiKey() now returns {id:'ID',key:'KEY'}

lnurl generateApiKey returns stringified JSON to allow piping to jq
Load server options from JSON file (CLI)
Move Lightning backend to separate file

Merge pull request #2 from chill117/datastores

Datastores: memory, redis, knex (sqlite/mysql/postgres)
